<item>
            <title>[LU-1439] Compatibility between client version 2.1 &amp; 2.2 and server version 1.8.4 (1.8.X)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1439</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We are wondering which kind of compatibility we can expect between clients versions 2.1 &amp;amp; 2.2 and a server running the 1.8.4 version.&lt;br/&gt;
Do we have to expect stability problems?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&amp;nbsp;- lustre servers version 1.8.4 &lt;br/&gt;
&amp;nbsp;- lustre clients versions 2.1 &amp;amp; 2.2</environment>
